'''Jjwaǧ''' neɣ '''zzwaǧ''' neɣ asali s teqbaylit, d asdukel n sin yemdanen deg yiwen wexxam. Asali yettili ger wergaz d tmeṭṭut. Tikkal yiwen wergaz d snat neɣ kraḍ neɣ ukkuẓ n tlawin. Acku Tineslemt d ddin n wagut n yiqbayliyen iwumi defka azref i wergaz akken ad-yaɣ ukkuẓ n tlawin maca ilaq ad-yesseɛdel gar-asent.

Iqbayliyen sseqdacen awal asali seg wemyag suli meḥsub zweǧ. Amedya : leflani yessuli axxam, meḥsub yezweǧ, yuɣ tamettut.

Win neɣ tin ara yessalin neqqar-as isli, tislit . asget islan, tislatin.
